{"tid":2507901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE身材擔當是她！Momo新畫報炸出「川」字腹肌，甜美外貌+火辣身材+帥氣魅力讓人淪陷","createTime":"2021-04-28T10:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T11:49:34.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9b1f1e3713dc6348cf4e3367b503e89012ba39d7","tid":2507901,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"韓國人氣女團Twice自出道以來就憑藉全員美貌出眾、清新俏麗的形象、琅琅上口的歌曲獲得大眾喜愛，每次回歸推出新作都能掀起網友討論，並獲得極好的成績，近日釋出的日文單曲《KURA KURA》，短短幾天，觀看人數就突破千萬，還被網友譽為是再創美貌巔峰。近日，舞蹈擔當成員Momo為韓國版時尚雜誌《W》合作，為日本運動品牌Onitsuka Tiger拍攝畫報，展現她獨有的帥氣性感，與多年習舞造就出的柔軟協調的身體。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/28/1/12188127.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F28%2F1%2F12188127.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=21e99abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/28/1/12188129.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F28%2F1%2F12188129.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=0d5860e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有可愛外貌的Momo，其實是獲成員們認證的Twice身材擔當，而近年隨著Twice風格的轉換，Momo也有較多展現自己身材優勢的機會，在這次公開的畫報中，Momo也不吝嗇展現出自己的緊實曲線，尤其是鮮明的腹肌線條，更是讓人驚嘆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/28/1/12188130.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F28%2F1%2F12188130.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=79386c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片中，Momo一連換了多套前衛時尚的運動風造型，包括黃色、黑色連身裙、藍橘撞色運動套裝、藍灰拼色長版外套、紅橘條紋裙裝，其中最令人印象深刻的非紅橘條紋裙裝莫屬，該造型大方露出她那沒有一絲贅肉的「川」字腹肌、筆直雙腿，擺出猶如芭蕾動作的姿勢，完美詮釋出運動時尚的魅力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/28/1/12188147.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F28%2F1%2F12188147.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=5daea509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/28/1/12188146.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F28%2F1%2F12188146.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=d02658eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說起Momo的好身材，她雖然沒有模特般的高挑身材，但自小練舞的關係造就她緊實的曲線，看上去比例極佳，不僅擁有22吋螞蟻腰、蘋果臀、筆直美腿，是許多人減肥時的目標榜樣。過去，Momo也曾在節目中公開分享自己的瘦身方法、腹肌養成祕訣，就是靠跳舞來消耗熱量，再搭配進階版的平板撐等雕塑運動打造曲線。而進階版的平板撐，就是先以雙手握拳與手臂呈90度的姿勢支撐，讓身體成一直線，再將下半身左右擺動，每次做50下，每天做3次。不過，這個動作需要一定的核心力量，大家執行時須小心，以免造成運動傷害。"},{"pid":"b6d34368bcc95725e1825c7d33195382e3f95209","tid":2507901,"uid":255310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"希澈蛇的肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7629c8c7d8ec9e51f085559885617bc630fcf22e","tid":2507901,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"希切老師..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f1172175f5d0dffd42da01676118d1b3abdbc4","tid":2507901,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6d34368bcc95725e1825c7d33195382e3f95209","tid":2507901,"uid":255310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:40:34.000Z"